---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Privacy Policy">
  <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto py-12 px-4">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="mb-4">
      We respect your privacy. This site does not sell your personal information or share it with
      third parties for marketing purposes. Basic information such as your email address (if you
      create an account) is used only for authentication and site functionality. We may use cookies
      or similar technologies for login sessions and analytics to improve your experience. By using
      this site, you agree to this simple privacy policy.
    </p>
    <p>
      If you have any questions or concerns, please contact us using the information on the About
      page.
    </p>
  </div>
</MainLayout>
